MasterChef UK - Series 12, Episode 5




In this heat, the contestants must attempt to impress 2012 champion Shelina Permalloo, and 2011 finalists Jackie Kearney and Sara Danesin Medio. After the four hopefuls have cooked, John and Gregg will decide which three contestants deserve to take the next step in the competition and go through to the quarter-final.




Original Air Date: 31-Mar-2016
